I'm Daniel, a software engineer hailing from Israel. I've been immersed in both frontend and backend development for over 5 years. Recently, I stumbled upon the world of creative coding and generative art, prompting me to make a shift to graphics programming. Over the last 2 years, I've been diving deep into this fascinating field. What I find most fulfilling about programming is its creative aspect, bringing visuals and aesthetically pleasing creations to life.
